i've owned my diaper dekor plus just under 2 years . first , i thought it worked fine . it easy deal , easy empty . first liner it came lasted me 6 months ( 1 baby - using newborn diapers through size 2 ) . however , unit failed control odors after 9 months . since then i've hide it various places my home keep odor minimum . definitely not convenien t.t he unit one particularly fundamental flaw regarding odor control . unlike diaper champ which allows you deposit diaper without opening container letting odors escape , diaper dekor no such provision . it two " trap doors " allow you drop diaper easily , then they supposed spring back into place . still , no matter how quickly you drop diaper , let top lid fall closed , strong odors inevitably escape . also , these " trap doors " quite flimsy . hinge one them recently broke so door no longer springs back into its closed position , thereby contributing odor problem . i inquired replacement regal lager they said i could purchase one $10 . instead i decided purchase new diaper champ , since i've pretty much it this thing . speaking flimsy , there two other flaws i've experienced . firstly , plastic foot pedal cracked seems loose . it still works , but i wonder how much longer . also , door bottom unit enables you cut off bag remove it not close very tightly , once again contributing lack odor control . door only held shut small plastic latch , leaving significant gap odors escape . overall , i not impressed diaper dekor plus . however , contrary what some people say regarding liner refills , actually never one my bigger complaints . i not find them cost-prohibitive all , because you get 3 liners $20 i found 3 liners last me 6 months holding toddler-size diapers . 1 year 9 months i've owned this system , i've only purchase refills twice . only thing i didn't like it i find it inconvenient purchase liners online ( couldn't find any local store carried them ) wait them shipped me , especially when there no indication when you reach end your last liner . diaper dekor only system i used extensively , i would not buy it again nor recommend it anyone . i'm hoping my diaper champ serve me better
